91d7cdfa8c890eb5782171a46e70896a81893ca477499fdbe9f6683af376043ee7fe3172ad90f5db1e08c43a11441504ad552083ea8d42dc9d88267a483e7e58  0001-Fix-segfault-when-importing-iCal-files.patch
"
